{
    "AWSTemplateFormatVersion" : "2010-09-09",
    "Description"              : "**Version 1.0** STEP-4 This template creates and installs an SharePoint Web Frontend Server WFE into a subnet inside a VPC. Default Domain Administrator password will be the one retrieved from the instance.  For adding members to the domain, ensure that they are launched in the domain member security group created by the Step-1 Infrastructure template and then configure them to use the AD instances private IP addresses as the DNS server. **WARNING** This template creates Amazon EC2 Windows instance and related resources. You will be billed for the AWS resources used if you create a stack from this template.",
