        "SPLicensekey" : {
            "Description" : "A valid SharePoint PID in the format VK7BD-VBKWR-6FHD9-Q3HM9-6PKMX. You can download a SharePoint 2010 trial and trail PID from http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=16631",
